CustomField.description: If filled out and Is Rollup Logging Enabled is checked off, Rollup will use the class with the name provided here to log. The class must conform to the IRollupLogger interface; check the README for more info. If left blank and logging is enabled, rollup log info will only be stored in the Apex debug logs.
